    "body": "It seems to work (when I do `runtest.py class`, although I haven't tested it any more thoroughly than that).  I'm not proposing to add extra CI runs or promise any level of support - just not to block it if people chose to set it manually. This is the same as what we do for PyPy.\r\n\r\nAlso contains a small tidy-up to https://github.com/cython/cython/commit/df5d541ad61ff3626b19dff7c8e38f2b9c4d4a25",
